-- Hydrobudowa, Partners Seek Extra Compensation for Motorway Order
-- B y   M a r e k   S t r z e l e c k i
-- 2012-07-26T16:33:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-26/hydrobudowa-partners-seek-extra-compensation-for-motorway-order.html
Hydrobudowa Polska SA (HBP) , the Polish
building company under court protection from creditors, and its
partners are seeking 270.1 million zloty ($80.2 million) in
extra compensation to continue work on the A4 motorway, the
company said today.  Hydrobudowa and its partners yesterday withdrew from the
original 1.4 billion-zloty contract to build the motorway
section in southeastern  Poland .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marek Strzelecki in Warsaw at 
